Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.04,0:02:30.06,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(641,400)\bord0.5\blur15\fs80\frz0\pos(1525,860)}You Better...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.70,0:02:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.78,0:02:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we had both resolved to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Your power is still needed here!
Dialogue: 0,00:02:46.66,00:02:48.63,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,どうしてだ？
Dialogue: 0,00:02:48.63,00:02:51.30,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,互いに覚悟はもう…。
Dialogue: 0,00:02:51.30,00:02:54.80,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,お前の力は まだ今ここで必要だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to rebuild chakra again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.87,0:02:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, let's teleport to\Nthe Root Time-Space...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.83,0:03:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll recover faster there, too.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:02.01,00:03:05.96,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ゼツ)いったん チャクラを練り直しか。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you do this\Nfor someone useless like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.83,0:03:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind that.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:05.96,00:03:09.17,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,母さん 始球空間へ飛ぼう。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakashi, be wary of the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:09.17,00:03:12.03,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あそこなら回復も早い。
Dialogue: 0,00:03:12.03,00:03:15.72,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なぜ 役にも立たない俺のために？
Dialogue: 0,00:03:15.72,00:03:20.22,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そんなことより\N敵に注意しろ カカシ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.83,0:03:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naruto, Sasuke, and Sakura...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.91,0:03:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is a crucial time for them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.45,0:03:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kakashi, you must survive{\i0}\N{\i1}and support the next generation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:03:32.65,00:03:37.03,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《ナルト サスケ そして サクラか。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.53,0:03:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's too soon for you to die.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:03:37.03,00:03:40.38,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,こいつらは今 大切なときだ。
Dialogue: 0,00:03:40.38,00:03:44.69,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,カカシ お前は\N新しい世代の支えとして→
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's totally useless, Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:44.69,00:03:46.99,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,まだ死ぬには早い》
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.62,0:03:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a goner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll rot away like trash and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.70,0:03:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough, Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:51.34,00:03:55.36,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ゼツ)そんなことをしてもムダだ ナルト。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.62,0:03:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.87,0:03:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't waste your chakra.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:55.36,00:03:58.05,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そいつはもうダメだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.58,0:04:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you sympathize with him?
Dialogue: 0,00:03:58.05,00:04:00.69,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ゴミのように朽ちて死ぬ。
Dialogue: 0,00:04:00.69,00:04:04.73,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,よせ ナルト やつの言うとおりだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.74,0:04:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He was originally your enemy, right?
Dialogue: 0,00:04:04.73,00:04:07.72,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,チャクラをムダに使うな。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.45,0:04:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Then again,\Nhe's a traitor to us now.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:07.72,00:04:10.69,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なぜ そんなやつに肩入れする？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.91,0:04:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A loser on both sides.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:10.69,00:04:14.82,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そいつは もともと\Nお前らの敵だった男だろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.99,0:04:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hated and resented\Nby friend and foe alike,
Dialogue: 0,00:04:14.82,00:04:19.06,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,まぁ かといって\Nこちらとしても裏切られた→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.45,0:04:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,with no one to call\Ncomrade or family...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.99,0:04:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He's alone, with nothing left.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:19.06,00:04:22.08,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,どっちつかずのクズだがな。
Dialogue: 0,00:04:22.08,00:04:25.74,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,敵味方双方から忌み嫌われ→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He's lost everyone precious to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.33,0:04:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and he can't realize his dreams.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:25.74,00:04:29.21,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,悲しんでくれる\N仲間も肉親もいない。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And after being used up,\Nhe's helpless at the end...
Dialogue: 0,00:04:29.21,00:04:32.59,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そいつは独り 何も残らない。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a fool, filled with\Nnothing but mistakes...
Dialogue: 0,00:04:32.59,00:04:37.40,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,大切な人を亡くし\N夢を叶えることもできず→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done nothing but—!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,00:04:37.40,00:04:41.32,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,利用されたあげく\N最後にうろうろと→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.74,0:04:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin... again...
Dialogue: 0,00:04:41.32,00:04:44.64,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,失敗だらけのマヌケか。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll create a world where\Nwe can be together again.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:44.64,00:04:47.45,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ナルト)てめえ さっきから…。\Nそうだな。
Dialogue: 0,00:04:49.57,00:04:52.49,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,((オビト : リン もう一度…。
Dialogue: 0,00:04:52.49,00:04:57.30,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,もう一度\Nキミのいる世界をつくろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.08,0:04:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shall...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:04:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sever the nexuses...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.66,0:05:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}of this world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:05:04.92,00:05:10.90,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《俺が この世の因果を→
Dialogue: 0,00:05:10.90,00:05:13.40,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,断ち切る》
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Now go on...
Dialogue: 0,00:05:27.53,00:05:30.83,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(マダラ)あ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.74,0:05:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Until I will be revived...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.91,0:05:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You shall be...
Dialogue: 0,00:05:36.30,00:05:43.50,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,さぁ 動け 俺が復活するまでの間。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.78,0:05:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.87,0:05:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Madara Uchiha.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:43.50,00:05:45.65,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,お前が…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.91,0:05:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But a world of just\Nvictors, peace, and love...
Dialogue: 0,00:05:45.65,00:05:48.21,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(長門)誰だ？
Dialogue: 0,00:05:48.21,00:05:51.01,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,うちはマダラだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a world can be created too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If you allow us to collaborate,\Nyou can learn how.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:53.82,00:05:58.48,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,勝者だけの世界\N平和だけの世界 愛だけの世界。
Dialogue: 0,00:05:58.48,00:06:02.23,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それらだけの世界を\Nつくることもできる。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.99,0:06:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Konan... Nagato.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:02.23,00:06:06.74,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,我々が協力すれば\Nそのやり方を知ることができる。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.49,0:06:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't trust these guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ever approach us again!
Dialogue: 0,00:06:11.48,00:06:15.56,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(弥彦)行くぞ 小南 長門。\Nこいつらは信用できない。
Dialogue: 0,00:06:15.56,00:06:18.66,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,二度と俺たちに近づくな。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.87,0:06:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll eventually realize it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.45,0:06:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.78,0:06:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You are going to be\Nvery useful to me.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:26.11,00:06:30.04,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,お前も いずれ\N気づくことになる。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.53,0:06:30.49,Signs,,0,0,0,,RIN NOHARA
Dialogue: 0,00:06:30.04,00:06:32.04,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ヤグラ)何やつだ！
Dialogue: 0,00:06:32.04,00:06:35.55,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,お前には せいぜい\N役に立ってもらうとしよう。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.78,0:06:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Summoning Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,00:06:47.39,00:06:49.36,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,口寄せの術！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Minato Sensei...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:07:22.13,00:07:25.13,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《ミナト先生…》
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I hereby declare the start of\Nthe Fourth Great Ninja War.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:08.95,00:08:12.96,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(我愛羅)あ～ あ…。
Dialogue: 0,00:08:15.57,00:08:21.17,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,第四次忍界大戦\Nここに 宣戦を布告する。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.58,0:08:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They each have formidable strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have even more\Nup my sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:35.46,00:08:38.03,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(カブト)どれも強者揃いだ。
Dialogue: 0,00:08:38.03,00:08:41.83,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それに 僕の持っている駒は\Nこれだけじゃない。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.20,0:08:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So be it.\NWe will join forces with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.91,0:08:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They will know despair thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:53.41,00:08:56.21,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,いいだろう 手を組んでやる。
Dialogue: 0,00:08:58.92,00:09:03.42,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,絶望を教えてやるのさ。 丁寧にな。
Dialogue: 0,00:09:11.34,00:09:13.45,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(みんな)うわ～！
Dialogue: 0,00:09:29.85,00:09:32.77,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,うっ… うわっ。
Dialogue: 0,00:09:32.77,00:09:35.77,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(うわ～っ！))
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.45,0:09:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.91,0:09:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an end worthy of\Nthe criminal that I am.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:44.03,00:09:46.90,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,お前の言うとおり→
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.53,0:09:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My Visual Prowess is back!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:09:46.90,00:09:50.40,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,罪人の俺に ふさわしい最後だ。
Dialogue: 0,00:09:54.40,00:09:57.00,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《サスケ : 瞳力が戻った》
Dialogue: 0,00:10:04.12,00:10:06.12,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,チッ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been here before!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she change worlds again?!
Dialogue: 0,00:10:14.80,00:10:17.36,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(サクラ)ここは前に来た…。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.58,0:10:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,00:10:17.36,00:10:19.86,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,また世界を変えたのか。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.62,0:10:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto, I'll handle\Nthe diversions this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He's beyond help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.58,0:10:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:26.06,00:10:28.78,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ナルト！
Dialogue: 0,00:10:28.78,00:10:31.49,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,今度は俺が陽動をかける。
Dialogue: 0,00:10:31.49,00:10:35.49,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そいつは もう助からん。\Nこっちへ来い。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,00:10:43.13,00:10:45.13,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,先に行く。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,00:10:53.13,00:10:57.94,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,くそっ くそっ… くそ～っ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.91,0:11:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Naruto
Dialogue: 0,00:11:10.13,00:11:14.44,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,もういい… ありがとうな ナルト。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.98,0:11:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,After fighting you,\NI feel like I've woken up.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:25.80,00:11:29.22,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(オビト)俺は お前と戦って→
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.48,0:11:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I are both powerless shinobi.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:29.22,00:11:32.53,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,何か目が覚めたような気がした。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.07,0:11:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,no, I should say everyone...
Dialogue: 0,00:11:36.87,00:11:40.76,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,((俺も お前も\Nしょせん 無力な忍だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.19,0:11:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,will eventually end up like me.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:40.76,00:11:43.45,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,お前も…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.77,0:11:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never end up like you!
Dialogue: 0,00:11:43.45,00:11:47.34,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,いや 誰でもいずれ→
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.86,0:11:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times\Ndo I have to tell you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.86,0:11:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,My dream is to become\Nthe Hokage!
Dialogue: 0,00:11:47.34,00:11:51.47,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺のようになるのだからな。
Dialogue: 0,00:11:51.47,00:11:55.51,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺は てめえみてえにはならねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no reason to keep on\Nfighting for a world like this.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:55.51,00:11:57.66,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,何度も言ってんだろ。
Dialogue: 0,00:11:57.66,00:12:00.47,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺がなりてえのは火影だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,In a few minutes,\Nthis world will be gone anyway.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:03.01,00:12:05.68,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,こんな世界のために→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you still fight?!
Dialogue: 0,00:12:05.68,00:12:09.64,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,もう戦う意味はないはずだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.19,0:12:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's my Ninja Way.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:09.64,00:12:14.24,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,この世界も数分で終わる。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.69,0:12:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I never go back on my word.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:16.18,00:12:19.26,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そうまでして なぜ戦う!?
Dialogue: 0,00:12:19.26,00:12:22.90,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,まっすぐ 自分の言葉は曲げねえ。
Dialogue: 0,00:12:22.90,00:12:26.20,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(それが 俺の忍道だからだ))
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.86,0:12:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't overdo it.\NLet's call it a day.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:32.20,00:12:36.51,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,((オビト : うおぉ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.57,0:12:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not giving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I make a promise?
Dialogue: 0,00:12:36.51,00:12:38.51,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,うわっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That I'm gonna become\Nthe Hokage!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,00:12:40.50,00:12:44.36,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(リン)無理しないで\N今日はここまでにしよう。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.69,0:12:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It was as if I saw my past self\Nwhen I looked at you.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:44.36,00:12:46.84,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,いや 俺は諦めねえ。
Dialogue: 0,00:12:46.84,00:12:50.89,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,約束したろ。\N俺は火影になるんだからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.65,0:12:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And I regret what I am now.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:50.89,00:12:53.54,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(もう…))
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But for some reason,\Nit also made me happy.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:53.54,00:12:57.55,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,まるでな お前を見ていると→
Dialogue: 0,00:12:57.55,00:13:03.11,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,昔の自分を見ているようで\N今の自分を後悔した。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.44,0:13:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,As a kid, I would imagine myself\Nas Hokage so often.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:03.11,00:13:08.22,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,だが 何よりそれが\Nなぜだか嬉しくもあってな。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.73,0:13:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That indescribable feeling\Nof exhilaration and anxiety...
Dialogue: 0,00:13:10.21,00:13:16.74,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,昔 ガキの頃は何度も\N火影になった自分を想像してよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you brought\Nthat all back for me.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:16.74,00:13:21.88,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,興奮と不安と\Nあの何とも言えぬ気持。
Dialogue: 0,00:13:21.88,00:13:28.84,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それを思い出させたからだろう。
Dialogue: 0,00:13:28.84,00:13:31.65,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,((２人 : はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.23,0:13:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry, Obito.\NYou'll get laughed at.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.86,0:13:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.07,0:13:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, the world of shinobi\Nis all about fighting.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:40.92,00:13:44.78,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ウッ…。\N泣くな オビト。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.69,0:13:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nowhere near\Na peaceful world.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:44.78,00:13:47.85,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そんなザマじゃ 笑われるぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.52,0:13:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll put an end to it,\Nno matter what.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:47.85,00:13:52.46,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,わかってる。\Nそれに 忍の世界は争いだらけだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.73,0:13:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're not the only ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.73,0:13:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget that we're here too.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:52.46,00:13:56.12,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,平和な世とは程遠い。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.07,0:13:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:56.12,00:13:59.92,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そんなもの\N俺が必ず終わらせてやる。
Dialogue: 0,00:13:59.92,00:14:03.46,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(アスマ)おい お前らだけじゃない。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.73,0:14:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin... I...
Dialogue: 0,00:14:03.46,00:14:05.94,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺たちもいることを忘れるなよ。
Dialogue: 0,00:14:05.94,00:14:09.04,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ああ そうだな。
Dialogue: 0,00:14:13.53,00:14:16.54,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,リン 俺は…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.86,0:14:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.19,0:14:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The higher-ups have decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.82,0:14:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Obito, you're going to be\Nthe next Hokage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're just as qualified...
Dialogue: 0,00:14:26.96,00:14:32.27,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(オビト)それは？\N(カカシ)上層部の決定だよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.86,0:14:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A supportive role suits me better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.86,0:14:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Rin would say\Nthe same thing.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:32.27,00:14:36.45,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,オビト お前が次の火影に決まった。
Dialogue: 0,00:14:36.45,00:14:39.54,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,だが 実力なら お前だって…。
Dialogue: 0,00:14:39.54,00:14:44.34,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺は サポート役が性に合ってる。\Nリンだって きっとそう言うさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you screw up,\NI won't hesitate
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to step up as a candidate\Nto become the next Hokage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.15,0:14:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.82,0:14:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,00:14:58.22,00:15:02.98,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,まっ お前がヘマをしたら 容赦なく\N次の火影に立候補するけどな。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:01.46,Signs,,0,0,0,,RIN NOHARA
Dialogue: 0,00:15:02.98,00:15:06.06,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なんだと？
Dialogue: 0,00:15:06.06,00:15:08.36,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,頑張れよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.82,0:15:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is driving me crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.65,0:15:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,All this paperwork\Nday in and day out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.27,0:15:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be helped...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the Hokage now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, something like this\Nsure beats having to fight every day.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:22.24,00:15:26.16,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,気がめいるな。\N来る日も来る日も書類 書類。
Dialogue: 0,00:15:26.16,00:15:31.42,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,しかたないだろ。\Nお前は火影なんだから。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:31.42,00:15:34.20,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,うへっ。\Nそれに この程度の雑務→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.82,0:15:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Hokage!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.19,0:15:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Hokage! Hello!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:34.20,00:15:37.29,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,戦いに追われる日々より\Nずっとマシだ。
Dialogue: 0,00:15:37.29,00:15:39.39,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,確かにな。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.94,0:15:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Hokage,\Nare you on your rounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.90,0:15:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.77,0:15:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.02,0:15:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just goofing off, right?
Dialogue: 0,00:15:42.55,00:15:45.05,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ハハッ。\N火影様！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:45.05,00:15:48.22,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,お疲れさまです。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna make something of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.02,0:15:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:48.22,00:15:52.10,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,火影様 見回りですか？\Nまあな。
Dialogue: 0,00:15:52.10,00:15:55.24,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,とか言って ほんとは\Nサボってるだけじゃねえの？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.77,0:15:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you hit only me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.77,0:15:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you were rude\Nto Lord Hokage!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:55.24,00:15:58.24,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,フン お前じゃあるまいし。\Nなんだと！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.98,0:15:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,00:15:58.24,00:16:03.37,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,やるのか？\Nやめなさい！\Nうぁ～っ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.15,0:16:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so peaceful, thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.57,0:16:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's everyone who did their best\Nto support the village.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:03.37,00:16:06.43,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,って なんで\N俺だけなんだってばよ！
Dialogue: 0,00:16:06.43,00:16:09.47,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(サクラ)だいたい\N火影様に対して失礼でしょ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be nice to talk\Nto Rin someday.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:09.47,00:16:12.42,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,まったく お前のおかげで\N平和なもんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.02,0:16:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:12.42,00:16:15.83,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺だけじゃない。\N今日まで里を支えてきた→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.02,0:16:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Imagining the village, friends,{\i0}\N{\i1}and me as the Hokage...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:16:15.83,00:16:18.80,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,みんなの力があってこそだ。
Dialogue: 0,00:16:18.80,00:16:22.11,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(いつか リンに話せるといいな。\Nああ))
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.40,0:16:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even after all that's happened...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.69,0:16:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just the thought of it seems to{\i0}\N{\i1}fill up the hole in my heart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:16:26.10,00:16:31.56,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(オビト)里があり 仲間がいて\N火影の俺がいると…。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because it's the end,
Dialogue: 0,00:16:31.56,00:16:34.62,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,いまさらな。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.86,0:16:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I find myself rambling all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:34.62,00:16:39.89,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,その想像するだけで 心の穴が\N埋まっていく気がしたよ。
Dialogue: 0,00:16:39.89,00:16:42.77,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,フッ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,00:16:42.77,00:16:48.27,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,最後だからか 俺は… 何をペラペラと。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.73,0:16:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't act tough and\Nhide your wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always watching you.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:52.77,00:16:54.77,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,((イタッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.73,0:16:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised me that\Nyou would become Hokage, Obito.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.73,0:17:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, I want to stop this war too.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:59.82,00:17:02.82,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(リン)強がって 傷を隠しても ダメ！
Dialogue: 0,00:17:02.82,00:17:05.86,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ちゃんと見てんだから。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.48,0:17:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I really want to save the world.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:05.86,00:17:10.62,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,オビトは 火影になるって\N私に約束した。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.73,0:17:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So I've decided to stick by\Nyour side and watch over you.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:10.62,00:17:14.76,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,いい？ 私だって\Nこの戦争を止めたい。
Dialogue: 0,00:17:14.76,00:17:18.20,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,世界を救いたいと\N本気で思ってるよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.32,0:17:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You told me saving you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.19,0:17:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,was the same as saving\Nthe world, remember?
Dialogue: 0,00:17:18.20,00:17:23.81,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,だから オビトのこと そばで\Nしっかり見守るって決めたの。
Dialogue: 0,00:17:25.89,00:17:31.39,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(リン)あなたを救うことは\N世界を救うのと同じなんでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.27,0:17:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I'm keeping\Nan eye on you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't hide anything\Nfrom me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Okay!
Dialogue: 0,00:17:37.16,00:17:39.13,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,うん…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.19,0:17:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Go for it, Obito!
Dialogue: 0,00:17:39.13,00:17:42.34,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,私が見張ってるってことは→
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.77,0:17:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Become Hokage and show me\Nhow you'll save the world.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:42.34,00:17:45.22,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,もう なんにも\N隠しごとはできないよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.98,0:17:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's another promise!
Dialogue: 0,00:17:45.22,00:17:47.85,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,うん！ うん！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.15,0:17:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,00:17:47.85,00:17:51.17,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,頑張れ オビト！
Dialogue: 0,00:17:51.17,00:17:55.56,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,火影になって かっこよく\N世界を救うとこ 見せてね！
Dialogue: 0,00:17:55.56,00:17:57.90,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それも 約束だよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.36,0:18:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot more suffering\Nlikely awaits you, Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:57.90,00:18:00.20,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(行こう))
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.15,0:18:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't ever change
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.19,0:18:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and hang on to your Ninja Way.
Dialogue: 0,00:18:07.95,00:18:13.88,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(オビト)お前には これから まだ\N多くの苦しみがあるだろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.82,0:18:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You once told me that
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,never going back on your word\Nis your Ninja Way, right?
Dialogue: 0,00:18:13.88,00:18:17.84,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,だが それでも\Nお前は変わることなく→
Dialogue: 0,00:18:17.84,00:18:21.21,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,その忍道を貫き通せ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.86,0:18:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,00:18:21.21,00:18:23.70,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,いつか 俺に言ったな？
Dialogue: 0,00:18:23.70,00:18:28.89,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,まっすぐ 自分の言葉は曲げない。\Nそれが俺の忍道だ…。
Dialogue: 0,00:18:28.89,00:18:30.93,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,だったかな？
Dialogue: 0,00:18:30.93,00:18:32.93,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あぁ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.23,0:18:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You better...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.52,0:18:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,become Hokage!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.69,0:18:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,00:18:42.71,00:18:45.29,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ナルト！
Dialogue: 0,00:18:45.29,00:18:50.30,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,お前は 必ず 火影になれ。
Dialogue: 0,00:18:52.31,00:18:54.31,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.98,0:19:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The vermin traitor has\Nfinally died, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He was vermin and\Npersistent as a cockroach.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:39.47,00:19:41.47,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,フッ！
Dialogue: 0,00:19:44.63,00:19:48.52,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ゼツ)裏切り者の虫ケラが\Nやっと死んだか。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.86,0:19:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't laugh at Obito!
Dialogue: 0,00:19:48.52,00:19:53.43,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,虫ケラは 虫ケラでも\Nこのしつこさは ゴキブリだったな。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.90,0:19:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.86,0:19:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep resisting,
Dialogue: 0,00:19:53.43,00:19:55.50,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ハハハハハ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.27,0:19:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll end up pitifully crumbling\Nto ash just like him!
Dialogue: 0,00:19:55.50,00:19:58.30,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,オビトを笑うな。
Dialogue: 0,00:20:00.28,00:20:02.31,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ナルト…。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.90,0:20:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,As someone who tried\Nto become Hokage,
Dialogue: 0,00:20:02.31,00:20:06.94,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ナルト… お前も\Nこれ以上 刃向かってると→
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.86,0:20:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Obito is nothing but...
Dialogue: 0,00:20:06.94,00:20:11.70,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,崩れて灰になった 哀れでみじめな\Nそいつと同じになるんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.15,0:20:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,awesome to me!
Dialogue: 0,00:20:11.70,00:20:16.30,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,火影になろうとしたオビトは\N俺には…。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.57,0:20:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:18.30,00:20:20.37,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,00:20:20.37,00:20:22.47,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,かっこよくしか見えねえよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.52,0:20:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I made you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems you got lost along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.15,0:20:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,00:20:27.46,00:20:29.50,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,((リン…。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.86,0:20:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of things happened\Nbefore I could come here.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:29.50,00:20:31.51,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,待ってたよ。
Dialogue: 0,00:20:31.51,00:20:34.96,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(オビト)そうか。 待たせて すまねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.82,0:20:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin, you know...
Dialogue: 0,00:20:34.96,00:20:38.09,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(リン)いろいろ\N道に迷ったみたいだね。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.44,0:20:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that promise I made to you...
Dialogue: 0,00:20:38.09,00:20:42.59,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あぁ… ここに来るまで\Nいろいろ あってよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.98,0:20:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you did your best!
Dialogue: 0,00:20:44.48,00:20:47.19,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,リン…。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.94,0:20:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been watching you all along!
Dialogue: 0,00:20:47.19,00:20:51.15,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺 リンとの約束…。
Dialogue: 0,00:20:51.15,00:20:53.50,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ううん。
Dialogue: 0,00:20:53.50,00:20:55.50,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,オビトは頑張ったじゃない。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.57,0:20:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,00:20:57.91,00:21:01.21,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ずっと 見てたんだよ。
